headline: Principal® named one of the 2025 World’s Most Ethical Companies by Ethisphere
summary: DES MOINES, Iowa, March 11, 2025--Principal Financial Group® has been recognized as one of the 2025 World’s Most Ethical Companies® by Ethisphere, a global leader in defining and advancing the standards of ethical business practices. This marks the 14th time Principal has received this prestigious honor, recognizing its dedication to ethical leadership and corporate responsibility.
